name: Hades style textual inversion
description:
Textual Inversion trained on art from the Hades game, tested on Anything V3 model. Put this TI in the embeddings folder, type "Hades-8500" in prompt to activate. Also I recommend to use words "realistic", "cartoon", "comic", "dark outlines" for better results.

UPD: Also sometimes it can generate dialogue boxes, so I advice to add "gameplay mechanics" to the negative prompt

modelVersions.name: Hades 65800
modelVersions.description: Updated version, better dataset and more steps were used for training
